infos.value: ...What's the matter?
The stars have grown faint.
It's a sign of the approaching dawn.
Right.
Aren't you tired?
Hehehe. Are you actually worried about little ole me?
We haven't had a proper night's rest since Leonis.
There's not much we can do about that.
Lady Mach√©rie waits imprisioned within Leonis Castle. If we don't reach her soon...
I know. That's why rest is a luxury we don't have right now.
But alas...
I hope Lady Glaciela is okay...
Don't worry. Viktora said that she would explain why we had to postpone.
...Do you believe her?
Huh?
I think your feelings for her might be clouding your judgement.
I-I-I don't have f-f-feelings for...
You don't trust her, do you?
I don't have any proof that she's lying.
But my intuition tells me so.
We need to hurry so that we can get back to Wezette Castle as soon as possible.
That's all we can do for now.
That we can agree on.
